createChainSpecificProxyWithNonce(addres.details: Allows the creation of a new proxy contract that should exist only on a single network (e.g. specific governance or admin accounts)      by including the chain ID in the `CREATE2` salt. Such proxies cannot be created to the same address on other networks by replaying the transaction.

params._singleton: Address of singleton contract. Must be deployed at the time of execution.
params.initializer: Payload for a message call to be sent to a new proxy contract.
params.saltNonce: Nonce that will be used to generate the salt to calculate the address of the new proxy contract.

createChainSpecificProxyWithNonceL2(addr.details: Allows to create a new proxy contract that should exist only on 1 network (e.g. specific governance or admin accounts)      by including the chain id in the create2 salt. Such proxies cannot be created on other networks by replaying the transaction.      Emits an extra event to allow tracking of `initializer` and `saltNonce`.

params._singleton: Address of singleton contract. Must be deployed at the time of execution.
params.initializer: Payload for a message call to be sent to a new proxy contract.
params.saltNonce: Nonce that will be used to generate the salt to calculate the address of the new proxy contract.

params._singleton: Address of singleton contract. Must be deployed at the time of execution.
params.initializer: Payload for a message call to be sent to a new proxy contract.
params.saltNonce: Nonce that will be used to generate the salt to calculate the address of the new proxy contract.

createProxyWithNonceL2(address,bytes,uin.details: Emits an extra event to allow tracking of `initializer` and `saltNonce`.

params._singleton: Address of singleton contract. Must be deployed at the time of execution.
params.initializer: Payload for a message call to be sent to a new proxy contract.
params.saltNonce: Nonce that will be used to generate the salt to calculate the address of the new proxy contract.

returns._0: The ID of the current chain as a {uint256}.

proxyCreationCode().details: The returned creation code can be used to compute a {SafeProxy} creation address.

proxyCreationCodehash(address).details: The returned creation codehash can be used to compute a {SafeProxy} creation address.

params.singleton: Address of the singleton contract that the proxy will delegate calls to.

createChainSpecificProxyWithNonce(addres.notice: Deploys a new chain-specific proxy with `_singleton` singleton and `saltNonce` salt. Optionally executes an initializer call to a new proxy.

createChainSpecificProxyWithNonceL2(addr.notice: Deploys a new chain-specific proxy with `_singleton` singleton and `saltNonce` salt. Optionally executes an initializer call to a new proxy.

createProxyWithNonce(address,bytes,uint2.notice: Deploys a new proxy with `_singleton` singleton and `saltNonce` salt. Optionally executes an initializer call to a new proxy.

createProxyWithNonceL2(address,bytes,uin.notice: Deploys a new proxy with `_singleton` singleton and `saltNonce` salt. Optionally executes an initializer call to a new proxy.

getChainId().notice: Returns the ID of the chain the contract is currently deployed on.
